content: 由Bigbry在2011年底提出的Dubstep子流派，结合了Dubstep/Brostep与Trap音乐的元素，如Trap风格的High·hat Pattern和808低音。也叫ElecTrap。
contentEn: Subgenre of Dubstep coined by Bigbry in late 2011 early 2012 that combines Dubstep with elements of Trap music such as Trap-style Highhat patterns and 808 sub. Also called ElecTrap.
